{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_06_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 06 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そう、そこでスピードを落とさない！\nかつ、丁寧に指先まで意識する！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's it! Don't slow down there!\nAnd be conscious of your fingertips with precision!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.2377291677999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 6.4243958155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4243958155,
      "endTime": 8.8287721316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 9.0287721435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "いいね、二人ともだんだん出来てきたよ\nこころは歯を見せなければ、もっといい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good‚ you're both getting the hang of it.\nKokoro‚ it would be even better if you didn't show your teeth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0287721435,
      "endTime": 14.8287721434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 15.0221055149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "え、笑顔だけは、やめませ～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh‚ but I won't stop smiling~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0221055149,
      "endTime": 19.4221054195,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4593.333228400001,
          "startTime": 19.6154387433
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 19.6154387433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、もうこんな時間\n二人ともいいわ、休憩よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it's already this late.\nAlright‚ you two‚ take a break!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20,
      "endTime": 24.6785845715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 24.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はひ～～っ！　や、やっと休めます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gasps F-finally‚ a break!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "endTime": 29.145668903999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 29.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、こころは、もう動けません～……\n今日はここまでにして、遊びに行きたいです～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant I-I can't move anymore~…\nLet's stop here for today and go have some fun~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3333333333,
      "endTime": 39.0375862557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 39.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカに来たのに、おはようからおやすみまで\n先輩と一緒に特訓なんてあんまりです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We came all the way to America‚ and yet from morning till night‚\nall we do is train with senpai! It's too much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "endTime": 45.9442531704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 46.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、僕達、他にやることないんだよね\nこっちで仕事がなんにもないし。ねえ、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we don't have anything else to do‚ right?\nWe don't have any work here. Right‚ Rio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1333333333,
      "endTime": 53.1692514697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 53.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、渡米した日に社長に問い合わせて\n私もさすがに驚いたわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I contacted the president on the day we arrived‚ and\neven I was surprised…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4,
      "endTime": 59.4788428742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 60.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 60.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "社長、神崎です。至急お話したいことがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "President‚ it's Kanzaki. I need to speak with you urgently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7,
      "endTime": 65.49627089500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 65.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6666666667,
      "endTime": 67.0283110024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "渡米初日から、もう問題でも起きたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did something happen already‚ on your first day in America?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333333333,
      "endTime": 69.77311755400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "問題なんてレベルじゃありません！\n社長、このアパートはなんですか？！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is beyond a mere problem!\nPresident‚ what is this apartment?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666666667,
      "endTime": 74.9300967015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 75.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、君達の居住スペースだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naturally‚ it's your living space.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1333333333,
      "endTime": 78.2232365173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その地域で一番治安のいい場所だ。安心していい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the safest area in that region. You can rest assured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "endTime": 82.6155387995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 82.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな心配はしてません！　まずこっちのエージェント\nと話をさせて下さい！　仕事はどうするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not what I'm worried about! First‚ let me speak\nwith the agent here! What about our work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8,
      "endTime": 89.8238304892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達のエージェント？　そんな者はいない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your agent? There's no such person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0333333333,
      "endTime": 93.8628364446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が用意したのは、君達の生活費とそのアパートだけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only prepared your living expenses and that apartment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8666666667,
      "endTime": 98.9538980601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 99.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？\nだったら私達はどこでパフォーマンスをするんですか？\nマネージャーは？　レッスンだって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nThen where are we supposed to perform?\nWhat about a manager? And lessons――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1666666667,
      "endTime": 105.72741256559999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分達で考えたまえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think about it yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "endTime": 107.916553243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 108.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1333333333,
      "endTime": 108.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達が一流のパフォーマーだというなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're truly top performers‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1,
      "endTime": 112.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どんな状況でも人々を魅了しステージに上がれるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "then you should be able to captivate people and get on stage in any situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1,
      "endTime": 116.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 116.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達の実力とやらに期待している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have high hopes for your so-called abilities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7333333333,
      "endTime": 119.89999999989999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good luck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9,
      "endTime": 120.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 120.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい、社長\nまだ話は終わって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ president.\nWe're not done talking――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666666667,
      "endTime": 123.8666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_apartment",
      "startTime": 124.0666666667
